  lines:
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: fbe0e12a368207d42aadf48040e4ab93, type: 2}
    text: ' Yes, is there a problem?'
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: ceb1a7909d01705478cf655dbaaaee6e, type: 2}
    text: No! Of course not, I was just watching you play, and I must say that I
      was very fascinated.
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: fbe0e12a368207d42aadf48040e4ab93, type: 2}
    text: "Fascinated? I mean, it\u2019s only Blackjack, I don\u2019t think winning
      a few rounds is that impressive\u2026"
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: ceb1a7909d01705478cf655dbaaaee6e, type: 2}
    text: 'You can say that, but that stack of chips you won over there says it all!

'
